data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom, two story home located in Breckinridge Forest! Enjoy newely upgraded Wood like flooring on the first floor that covers the large living room with a beautiful fireplace. Your spacious kitchen has ample cabinet space and offers a large walk in pantry/utility room. The primary suite features a generous sized bathroom complete with double sinks, separate shower, soaking tub and huge walk in closet. Create great memories in your roomy game room upstairs. Another bonus, check out the huge backyard perfect for hosting events or creating your backyard paradise!     Contact me today!
